<title>NaŐĪ pi apel čchi yok čt ∆≤IT65</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 NaŐĪ pi apel čchi yok čt
 Chihowa hak oke;
 Im isht ai iŐĪ kana yoka
 Pilla pihiŐĪm čshke.

[V2]
 Chekosi fehna apel čt
 Yukpahanli hoke;
 Im isht hlampko yaŐĪ k čllochit
 Ishit pi eshishke.

[V3]
 NaŐĪ pal čmmi e pisakm čt,
 Chekosi fehna hoŐĪ
 Ai it apela achukma
 E pihiŐĪsa hoke.

[V4]
 Chihowa ai aŐĪhli fehna,
 Y čmmak bieka hosh
 NaŐĪ pi apel čchi yoke;
 Inla m čt ikshoshke.

[V5]
 Yakni, n čnih chaha mom čt,
 Okh čta chito yaŐĪ
 Ik oka-k čnia kia
 Sa nukshoyupa wa.

[V6]
 Okhina y čt b čchaŐĪy čshke,
 Mih yoŐĪ a yan čllit
 AŐĪya hosh, okla moma ka
 Yukpala chiŐĪ hoke.</lyrics>
<aka>God a Refuge in trouble</aka>
<hymn_number>65</hymn_number>
</song>